    • version

      void version(eu.openminted.registry.domain.VersionInfo versionInfo, io.github.agroportal.ncboproxy.model.NCBOOutputModel outputModel)
      Set the version of the resource based on the version property from the Bioportal JSONLD output. The resource revisions and revision dates from the OMTDShare specification correspond to different concepts than submissions in bioportal and thus cannot be encoded here.
      Parameters:
      versionInfo - The version info complex type JAXB binding
      outputModel - The NCBO Output Model for the ontology submission

    • contactInformation

      void contactInformation(eu.openminted.registry.domain.ContactInfo contactInfo, io.github.agroportal.ncboproxy.model.NCBOOutputModel ncboOutputModel)
      Set the contact information metadata setting the contactInfo complex type that contains the contact point and the list of contact for the resource. In bioportal there is no way of differentiating between contact persons and contact organizations, therefore, by default, all contacts are treated as contact persons.
      Parameters:
      contactInfo - The contact information JAXB complex type
      ncboOutputModel - The NCBO Output Model for the ontology submission
